CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 27, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Flower Girl - Little Marge Sweetvine Gaillard, guest of Mrs. Williams of 717 Finland Street, took time out from her visit to be flower girl in a mock wedding held at Central Baptist Church recently. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Marge Sweetvine Gaillard wearing light colored ruffled dress, and holding light colored crocheted purse, standing in front of ornately carved lectern in Central Baptist Church for mock wedding
